headline: Jim Cramer Expresses Shock Over Stanley Black & Decker’s Weak Quarter
summary: Stanley Black & Decker, Inc. (NYSE:SWK) is one of the stocks Jim Cramer recently talked about. During the episode, Cramer discussed the company’s earnings in light of tariffs. He said: “Oh, and if that wasn’t enough, Stanley Black & Decker, another name, look in your house, you’ve got these, really, just whoa, it shocked me. […]
